column2: SELECT ALL ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY s.ra ASC) as RowNumber, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, u,dered_u, g,dered_g, r,dered_r, i,dered_i, p.z as z1, dered_z as dered_z1, deVRad_u, deVRad_g, deVRad_r, deVRad_i, deVRad_z as deVRad_z1, flags_r, petroR9#_r, petroR5#_r, petroR9#_r/petroR5#_r as c FROM Galaxy AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid Where s.class=&&&  AND s.zwarning=# AND s.z<# AND (petroR9#_r/petroR5#_r)=#
